At night, the apparitions are mostly frightening.
If she waits for sleep in her dark room, which comes much too rarely and far too late, she often cannot distinguish whether she is awake or already dreams of whether the pictures she sees are made of the fractures or the girl with the bleeding cuts of arms and legs, in front of her open or closed eyes.
Leave me alone, she screams at the shapes.
