With the transparency of the products that Audatex offers, you can easily get an overview of the type of support it gives to industry experts.
This company offers ten different tools, with the star of the products AudaPlus, a standard solution for the assessment of accidents for the assessors.
It includes vehicles, motorcycles and light and heavy industrial vehicles.
In addition to the cost of the parts, it includes the estimated repair times or the painting prices of the manufacturer.
This tool is paid according to the purpose of use, i.e. for each opinion.
